19;s seven hills and can be seen from pretty much anywhere. Its beautiful architecture remains somewhat unnoticed as the majority of the visitors only visit the Blue Mosque.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Discover Istanbul through food:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/istanbul-food-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Taste of two continents food tour<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/best-things-to-do-istanbul-Suleymaniye-Mosque.jpg\" alt=\"best things to do istanbul Suleymaniye Mosque\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"best things to do istanbul Suleymaniye Mosque\" class=\"wp-image-14383 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135128\/best-things-to-do-istanbul-Suleymaniye-Mosque.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135128\/best-things-to-do-istanbul-Suleymaniye-Mosque-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135128\/best-things-to-do-istanbul-Suleymaniye-Mosque-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135128\/best-things-to-do-istanbul-Suleymaniye-Mosque-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135128\/best-things