<p>A short 10-minute walk to the river through the lively streets of Istanbul brings you to the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/egypt\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Egyptian<\/a> Spice Bazaar. A large bazaar of shops selling spices, nuts, oils, sweets, jewelry, and dried fruits. During religious and public holidays, the bazaar is closed. <\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/14277&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/18150305\/istanbul-turkey.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/18150305\/istanbul-turkey-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/18150305\/istanbul-turkey-347x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"11 Best Things To Do in Istanbul, Turkey\" height=\"600\" width=\"347\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p><strong>Tip: <\/strong>On your way to the Spice Bazaar, visit the Rustem Pasha Mosque. During our visit, it wasn&#x2019;t accessible due to construction, but we&#x2019;ve heard great stories about it.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Find all:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/istanbul-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\">Hotels in Istanbul<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/istanbul-spice-bazaar-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"istanbul spice bazaar\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"istanbul spice bazaar\" class=\"wp-image-14381 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135134\/istanbul-spice-bazaar-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135134\/istanbul-spice-bazaar-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135134\/istanbul-spice-bazaar-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135134\/istanbul-spice-bazaar-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135134\/istanbul-spice-bazaar-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads