USD). Don&#x2019;t buy any skip-the-line tickets on the street. <a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/istanbul-hagia-sophia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Order your tickets online<\/a> as the Hagia Sophia is the most popular to do in Istanbul.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Best of Istanbul?<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/best-of-istanbul-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Join the popular Istanbul tour.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/things-to-do-istanbul-Hagia-Sophia-667x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do istanbul Hagia Sophia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"278\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do istanbul Hagia Sophia\" class=\"wp-image-14405 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135025\/things-to-do-istanbul-Hagia-Sophia-667x810.jpg 667w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135025\/things-to-do-istanbul-Hagia-Sophia-300x365.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135025\/things-to-do-istanbul-Hagia-Sophia-600x729.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/05\/23135025\/thin